ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectRemission Order of Federal Administrative Fees Paid or Payable by the Yukon and the Northwest Territories
PrecisREMISSION ORDER in respect of federal administrative fees paid or to be paid by Yukon and the Northwest Territories (NWT) for set-up costs related to the rebate programs put in place by the territories to return the proceeds of carbon pollution pricing to their residents and businesses.
